---
By: Paul Toumier
Locus:
  Page: 339
  Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Oneness
---
Neurosis is always linked with an inability to evolve. The adult who cannot
accept growing old, or the old person who cannot accept his old age, or
accepts it grudgingly, ‘because he’s got to,’ is in the same difficulty,
blocked in his evolution against the stream of life.
